BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Toronto Social Events
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/toronto/
UID:event_313688629@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260326T030007Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260327T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260327T220000
SUMMARY:Language Exchange - Speak English & Speak Spanish Online
DESCRIPTION:Language Exchange Toronto - Se Habla English & Spanish\n**Span
 ish Language Conversation Toronto** is part of ***Se Habla***\, a worldwid
 e community made up of 9 Meetup groups from 9 different cities across 6 co
 untries. Join us and don't miss the opportunity to speak with native speak
 ers.\n\n**Five years of meeting online.** Don’t wait—become part of ou
 r supportive international network of like-minded people and make friends 
 all over the world. Free forever after One-Time Donation.\n\n**We meet on 
 the following days:**\n\n* Monday 8 pm\n* Wednesday 8 pm\n* Friday 8 pm\n*
  Sunday 11 am\n\n**Format**\nDepending on attendance and nationality\, sma
 ll groups are formed with 4-6 people:\n\n* 2 native English speakers\n* 2 
 native Spanish speakers\n* 1 native speaker of another language\n\nThe mee
 tings last for 2 hours and are divided into 4 periods:\n\n* 30 minutes spe
 aking in English\n* 30 minutes speaking in Spanish\n* 30 minutes speaking 
 in English\n* 30 minutes speaking in Spanish\n\nPlease note that **we spea
 k half of the time in English and half in Spanish.** We help each other le
 arn both languages.\n\n**After two hours**\, everyone returns to the main 
 room to meet all participants and take a group screenshot. If you have tim
 e\, you’re welcome to stay and continue the conversation for as long as 
 you like.\n\n**Community**\n**We have 9 MeetUp groups meeting at the same 
 time** (Mexico City\, Calgary\, Vancouver\, Toronto\, New York\, London\, 
 Los Angeles\, Medellin\, and Santiago de Chile). However\, during the exch
 ange\, you will meet people not only from these cities but also from all o
 ver the world.\n\nYou can get the link to our 9 MeetUp groups by visiting 
 any of the following pages:\n[https://se-habla.com/spanish-meetup/](https:
 //se-habla.com/spanish-meetup/)\n[https://se-habla.com/english-meetup/](ht
 tps://se-habla.com/english-meetup/)\n\n**One-Time Donation**\nFor over fou
 r years\, the meetings were free\, but starting last October\, I am reques
 ting a **ONE-TIME DONATION** to access the meetings and help to cover the 
 costs of the 9 MeetUp Groups.\n\nYou can make the one-time donation at the
  link below. Afterward\, PayPal will redirect you to a page where you'll f
 ind the Zoom link to join the meeting.\n[https://se-habla.com/language-exc
 hange/](https://se-habla.com/language-exchange/)\n\nIf you have already ma
 de a donation and don't have the Zoom link\, please contact me.\n\n**Pleas
 e don’t hesitate to reach out if you have any further questions.**\n\nSe
 e you soon\,\n**Héctor Fuentes**
